    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1280000031730044928",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年9月3日- 2025年9月9日，规则预计于 2025年9月10日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">&nbsp;核心调整点：</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;①细化类目乱挂的范围；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;②对类目乱挂的违规处理措施进行调整；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">修订后内容如下：</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>1、</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>【违规定义】</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>1.1 类目乱挂</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1.1 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">常规类目乱挂：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商品挂靠的类目，不符合类目释义，及类目经营范围</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1.2 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂实现少缴纳质保金：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂，逃避类目设定的质保金，如随身wifi错挂其他类目，少缴纳平台要求的质保金</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1.3 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂实现不当套利：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂，额外获取平台流量、补贴等，如乱挂商品到特定补贴品类上，获取额外的平台资源</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1.4 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂突破类目招商规则：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂，规避平台招商开放规则，如白酒不针对个人店开放招商，通过错挂类目，实现发品和售卖白酒</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1.5 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂逃避广告投放限制：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂，规避平台的投放限制，如成人用品乱挂到其他类目，实现广告投放</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1.6 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂逃避类目资质效验：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂，逃避类目资质效验，如将三类医疗器械商品，错挂到不需要效验类目资质的类目上</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1.7 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂混淆消费者购物决策：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过类目乱挂的行为，混淆消费者视听，给消费者带来体验损伤，例如在一个spu下错挂其他品类sku，用来实现低价引流</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">、【处置规则】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.1.1 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">违规程度轻微：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">违规商品预警，需在提示整改期内完成整改；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">2.1.2 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">违规程度一般：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">对于高频乱挂及预警后未做出整改的商家进行警告，平台有权针对违规商品，执行包括但不限于罚款、下架、或迁移到正确类目，视实际情况进行全店搜索、推荐流量降权、屏蔽；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">2.1.3 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">违规程度严重：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对拒不整改与蓄意对抗的商家进行，违规商品下架，及支付近30日全店商品销售额的20%作为违约金，最低1000元，禁发新品、禁止上架、页面止付、冻结钱包（执行视实际违规程度、违规后果，包括但不限于，通过类目乱挂恶意逃避，类目资质效验规则、招商资质标准、类目资费规则、类目广告禁投规则、非全新商品管理规则，及其他可能引起平台或用户损失和体验的违规）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">2.1.4 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">违规程度极其严重：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">对恶意对抗的商家进行全店商品下架，及</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">支付近30日全店商品销售额的20%作为违约金<span style=\"background: white;\">，最低3000元，禁发新品、禁止上架、页面止付、冻结钱包、类目停用、加收保证金、延长账期、</span>店铺清退等处理措施<span style=\"background: white;\">（</span>执行视实际违规程度、违规后果，包括但不限于，通过类目乱挂恶意逃避，类目资质效验规则、招商资质标准、类目资费规则、类目广告禁投规则、非全新商品管理规则，及其他可能引起平台或用户损失和体验的违规<span style=\"background: white;\">）；</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">2.1.5 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次（两次及以上）或，全店大量在售商品出现以上违规行为，或，存在关联店铺批量恶意违规，或，因上述行为引起重大投诉或舆情的，平台有权进行升级治理，包括对关联店铺的违规升级治理。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.6 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">严重违规场景示例，及京东开放平台类目规则附录</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #e03e2d; background: white;\">严重违规场景包括但不限于，如：白酒、虚拟充值、蓄电池、随身wifi、5G/4G上网、上网卡、办号卡、医疗器械、危化品、仿真枪、成人用品、化妆品、非全新商品挂新品类目、殡葬用品、卡券、农资园艺等商品，未挂靠在正确类目，实现逃避或突破平台的类目招商、资费、资质、非全新商品管理规则，具体类目规则见：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）京东开放平台个人/个体店铺开放招商类目范围：https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/hot-topic/detail?issueId=1000-45601.html</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）京东开放平台店铺开放招商类目范围：https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/45582.html</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）京东开放平台招商资质标准细则：https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=2614</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）京东开放平台类目资费规则：https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=638209647311982592</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）京东开放平台禁投广告的商品与服务：https://jzt.jd.com/school/course/detail?contentId=11271&amp;channelIds=1958</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）京东开放平台非全新商品管理规则：https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1257164497286729728</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）京东开放平台关联店铺管理规则：https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=4680</span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</p>",
